OL,3,CBillionaire halts Harvard donations as
OL,4,Cit produces 'whiny snowflakes'
OL,6,FA hedge fund billionaire who has
OL,7,Fdonated more than $500 million to over
OL,8,Fthe years has halted contributions to
OL,9,Fhis alma mater after claiming the
OL,10,Felite institution produces "whiny
OL,11,Fsnowflakes".
OL,13,FKen Griffin, one of the richest people
OL,14,Fin the world, joins a growing list of
OL,15,Fdonors to Harvard, the University of
OL,16,FPennsylvania, Columbia and other top
OL,17,Fschools who have decided to close
OL,18,Ftheir chequebooks.
