OL,3,CBillionaire halts Harvard donations as
OL,4,Cit produces 'whiny snowflakes'
OL,6,FAt a conference in Miami on Tuesday,
OL,7,FMr Griffin expressed deep frustration
OL,8,Fwith the state of American
OL,9,Funiversities.
OL,11,FThe founder of hedge fund Citadel, the
OL,12,F55-year-old said he is no longer
OL,13,Fsupporting Harvard financially but
OL,14,Fwould like that to change.
OL,16,FMr Griffin suggested that students at
OL,17,Felite schools are "just caught up in
OL,18,Fthe rhetoric of oppressor and
OL,19,Foppressee and... just like whiny
OL,20,Fsnowflakes."
