OL,6,F"Until Harvard makes it very clear
OL,7,Fthat they're going to resume their
OL,8,Frole as (educators of) young American
OL,9,Fmen and women to be leaders, to be
OL,10,Fproblem solvers, to take on difficult
OL,11,Fissues, I am not interested in
OL,12,Fsupporting the institution," he told
OL,13,FCNBC.
OL,15,FHarvard has not yet publicly commented.
