OL,6,FThe donor backlash at Ivy League
OL,7,Fschools, a group of eight prestigious
OL,8,Fprivate colleges and universities in
OL,9,Fthe US, raises questions about the
OL,10,Fsway wealthy individuals hold over
OL,11,Feducational institutions.
OL,13,FJust last April, Griffin made a $300
OL,14,Fmillion (#237m) gift to Harvard's
OL,15,FFaculty of Arts and Sciences.
