OL,6,FAt the time, the billionaire praised
OL,7,FHarvard as a "great institution" and
OL,8,Fhailed FAS for being "committed to
OL,9,Fadvancing ideas that will shape
OL,10,Fhumanity's future, while providing
OL,11,Fimportant insight into our past."
OL,13,FOver four decades, Griffin has donated
OL,14,Fmore than $500 million (#395m),
OL,15,FHarvard said at the time.
