OL,6,FThat includes a $150 million (#118m)
OL,7,Fcontribution to financial aid in 2014
OL,8,Fthat Harvard said holds the record for
OL,9,Fthe "largest single gift to
OL,10,Fundergraduate financial aid and to
OL,11,FHarvard College."
OL,13,FMr Griffin, who has built a fortune
OL,14,Fthat Bloomberg estimates is $37
OL,15,Fbillion, is now expressing concern
OL,16,Fabout the direction of elite schools
OL,17,Fand diversity, equity and inclusion
OL,18,Fpolicies (DEI).
