OL,3,CBillionaire halts Harvard donations as
OL,4,Cit produces 'whiny snowflakes'
OL,6,F"Will America's elite universities get
OL,7,Fback to the roots of educating
OL,8,FAmerican children - young adults - to
OL,9,Fbe the future leaders of our country
OL,10,For are they going to maintain being
OL,11,Flost in the wilderness of
OL,12,Fmicroaggressions and a DEI agenda that
OL,13,Fhas no real endgame," he said.
OL,15,FDEI policies have emerged as a
OL,16,Fflashpoint at major universities and
OL,17,Fin the business world, with some
OL,18,Farguing they have gone too far.
